A-Team Program Pseudo Code

Student Name:  Aaron Myra  
Program Title:  The A-Team

1. Initilize variables
2. Open the A-Team intro file
3. Read the A-Team intro file
4. For each line add a line number to the beginning
5. For each line determine the number of characters it contains
6. If line contains more than 20 characters change line to all lower case
7. If line contains less than 20 characters change line to all upper case
8. Import random function and generate random number
9. Omit the line in the A-Team into that matches the random number generated
10. Output the original text followed by the altered text.